CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 2, 1961, pg. 13A, reads: "LEAVING CHURCH - Mr. and Mrs. Richard M. Prunty are shown leaving the Sixth Mt. Zion Church, following their recent wedding. The bride is the former Romaine W. Henderson, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Mack Henderson Sr. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Groom Richard M. Prunty, and bride Romaine W. Henderson Prunty wearing lace gown with tiered skirt, posed behind three tiered wedding cake, in interior with boxes of Ritz crackers in background
